{"tid":1239196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集合大家力量] 關於TVB報導反送中一事, 我地可以向通訊事務管理局投訴","createTime":"2019-06-18T05:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T12:17:52.000Z","uid":217418,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2006279317bb797b73e60e466a03d6071e36ffa6","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:52:01.000Z","msg":"TVB(電視廣播有限公司)在反送中報導一事中，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB的報導完全扭曲事實，其內容嚴重偏袒警方和政府，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n<br />\n4. 警方違法向示威者投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些示威者向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n=<br />\n<br />\n<strong>投訴表格：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAeTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=1deaa797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\nCopy上面段野去投訴tvb!<br />\n(段野係朋友SD比我, 我自己改左少少 先放入投訴表格)<br />\n=<br />\n<br />\n發夢見到好多人用BT等方式 DL TVB節目, 等依間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公司少左收視 同廣告收益<br />\n<br />\n又或者選擇去睇其他電視台<br />\n=<br />\nby the way 亦都可以做下依個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[請願] 西人記者叫我地去寫信玩鳩兩個落order 打人既西人警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223477/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223477/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"388e5443a77fafd68949076fba39c6a3b6d50a7c","tid":1239196,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"009df1ebfeb95a5a5edb78f5ee47fc4724969eaa","tid":1239196,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"388e5443a77fafd68949076fba39c6a3b6d50a7c","tid":1239196,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦屌你老母，cut走晒前面個段"},{"pid":"7c13c049ded080a6711462bce9b16a942bb74a13","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:09:49.000Z","msg":"推, 繼續不合作運動!"},{"pid":"d3b80d1368be301fdc4480b4d2a8baddae76ded8","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"推, 抗爭到底!!"},{"pid":"057c5ecfdba782b66d24bb04169fef3f7ef2261a","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"TOP"},{"pid":"31575e35d9ff719c1a50c5b72cd484ef75a4da3a","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:49:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1540b7a3a18010dfb4014bfc56713091dbddc0a3","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41a2e6c73c156092de3aaac9e0d75d558cb98a53","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8643ea393d79b8917dcffbdd78e674348264f2d","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"Still Hong Kong, not China!"},{"pid":"9b19cfe0a0f2e55b9aea7099272b34d6627dc8e5","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:24:06.000Z","msg":"top"},{"pid":"ad093ebda1974417b7ebb56bed5b78993d7bbc82","tid":1239196,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"top"},{"pid":"9bc74cb71cfe38302c37bc2d8533ba434